---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'

import imageLogo0 from '@svg/logo-nuevo.svg'

import ContainerSection from '@ui/ContainerSection.astro'
---

<div class='bg-loafer-100 py-24' id='metodologia'>
  <ContainerSection>
    <div>
      <h2 class='text-center text-3xl font-bold text-eden-800 md:text-5xl'>Metodologia</h2>
      <p class='mx-auto mt-6 max-w-4xl text-center text-lg font-medium leading-snug text-eden-800'>
        Metodología de trabajo para acompañarte en el proceso de creación y desarrollo de tu negocio.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class='mt-20'></div>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2'>
      <div class='flex items-center justify-center h-full'>
        <figure class='bg-white rounded-xl aspect-[3/4] p-10 flex items-center justify-center'>
          <Image src={imageLogo0} alt='Hombre pensativo' class='rounded-lg' width={350} height={350} loading='lazy' />
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class='flex flex-col gap-8'>
        <!--================== PASO 1 - COMPONENTE ===================-->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap sm:justify-start sm:gap-8'>
          <div class='flex items-center'>
            <div class='flex size-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-jungle-green-600'>
              <Icon name='round-looks-one' class='size-12 text-jungle-green-600' />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center md:text-start flex flex-col items-start justify-center'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-eden-800'>Desafios</h3>
            <p class='pt-2 text-eden-800'>
              Identificamos los desafíos que enfrentas a diario y analizamos la situación actual del negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--================== PASO 2 - COMPONENTE ===================-->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap sm:justify-start sm:gap-8'>
          <div class='flex items-center'>
            <div class='flex size-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-jungle-green-600'>
              <Icon name='round-looks-two' class='size-12 text-jungle-green-600' />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center md:text-start flex flex-col items-start justify-center'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-eden-800'>Opciones</h3>
            <p class='pt-2 text-eden-800'>
              Analizamos las opciones disponibles y definimos un plan de acción personalizado para impulsar tu negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--================== PASO 3 - COMPONENTE ===================-->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap sm:justify-start sm:gap-8'>
          <div class='flex items-center'>
            <div class='flex size-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-jungle-green-600'>
              <Icon name='round-looks-three' class='size-12 text-jungle-green-600' />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center md:text-start flex flex-col items-start justify-center'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-eden-800'>Consecuencias</h3>
            <p class='pt-2 text-eden-800'>
              Analizamos las consecuencias de cada opción y definimos un plan de acción personalizado para impulsar tu
              negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--================== PASO 4 - COMPONENTE ===================-->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap sm:justify-start sm:gap-8'>
          <div class='flex items-center'>
            <div class='flex size-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-jungle-green-600'>
              <Icon name='round-looks-four' class='size-12 text-jungle-green-600' />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center md:text-start flex flex-col items-start justify-center'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-eden-800'>Soluciones creativas</h3>
            <p class='pt-2 text-eden-800'>
              Buscamos soluciones creativas y definimos un plan de acción personalizado para impulsar tu negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--================== PASO 5 - COMPONENTE ===================-->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-nowrap sm:justify-start sm:gap-8'>
          <div class='flex items-center'>
            <div class='flex size-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-jungle-green-600'>
              <Icon name='round-looks-five' class='size-12 text-jungle-green-600' />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center md:text-start flex flex-col items-start justify-center'>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-eden-800'>Conclusiones</h3>
            <p class='pt-2 text-eden-800'>
              Analizamos las conclusiones y definimos un plan de acción personalizado para impulsar tu negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ContainerSection>
</div>
